## Concurrency Tuning

`ai.concurrency` range 1-10 controls parallel AI subprocess count. Default `5` (changed to `2` in WSL environments per v0.4.8+ resource management constraints). Lower values recommended for resource-constrained environments (reduces memory pressure), higher values accelerate generation (increase throughput). Timeout `ai.timeoutMs` default `300000` (5 minutes) per file analysis subprocess, increase for large files or slow network connections.